Original Text: \Eじゃあみんな、行ってらっしゃい
Machine translation: \EWell then, everyone, take care and have a safe journey.

今回はここまでにしておこう…。

\EIt seems like it's impossible to go any further...

\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]It appears that continuing further is not feasible...

討伐の画面レイアウトを作ります
\Eここいらで休憩しておこう。

Machine translation: \EAre we ending the expedition around here...?
